              "sentence_index": 2
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "CoreWeave?",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 3
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "How are they connected to Nvidia, and what makes them a contender?",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
