              "sentence_text": "They're a key Nvidia partner, providing AI cloud services using Nvidia's technology.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 5
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Nvidia even increased its holding in CoreWeave by 95%.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 6
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "And their growth?",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 7
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "CoreWeave's revenue grew 112% to $2.1 billion in the first quarter of 2026.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 8
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "This is faster than Nvidia's 85% revenue growth in its first quarter, partly due to their smaller size.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 9
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "So, faster growth, but any downsides to this rapid expansion?",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 10
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "They reported a $740 million loss in the first quarter, and profitability is unlikely soon due to capital expenditures for a $99.4 billion backlog.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 11
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Still, their smaller size aids rapid growth.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 12
            }
