      "story_headline": "U.S. strikes Iran again as Trump says a deal is “close”",
      "story_dek": "Washington hits a second site inside Iran while Tehran tightens its grip on the Strait of Hormuz.",
      "story_segment_slug": "geopolitics",
      "story_primary_outlet_name": "CNN",
      "story_first_reported_utc": "2026-05-30T23:41:37.823662+00:00",
      "segments": {
        "segment_label": "Geopolitics"
      },
      "digests": [
        {
          "digest_id": "3cc05d55-53ae-4e87-9dbf-49662fe2df53",
          "digest_audio_url": "https://cerfennlcgureyifraqy.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/digest-audio/digest-1.mp3",
          "caption_sentences": [
            {
              "sentence_text": "The U.S. military hit another target inside Iran overnight — a site Washington says threatened American forces and commercial shipping.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 0
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "And President Trump says he's confident a deal to end the fighting is close.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 1
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "But \"close\" isn't \"done.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 2
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Right — he made clear he's not satisfied with the terms yet.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 3
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "And he's willing to restart strikes if Iran doesn't meet U.S. demands.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 4
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Meanwhile Tehran is pushing back hard.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 5
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "It just issued new rules for any ship trying to pass through the Strait of Hormuz.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 6
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "That's the chokepoint where about a fifth of the world's oil moves.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 7
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Iran's trying to formalize control over it — defying U.S. warnings.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 8
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "So a ceasefire is being talked up, and a flashpoint is heating up — at the same time.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 9
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "We'll see which one wins.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 10
            }
          ],
          "digest_is_current": true,
          "digest_duration_ms": 50611,
          "digest_ambient_poster_url": "https://cerfennlcgureyifraqy.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/story-posters/digest-1.png"
        }
      ]
