              "sentence_index": 6
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "Still under wraps.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 7
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "But the message is clear — top athletes aren't just playing the game anymore.",
              "anchor_speaker": "JORDAN",
              "sentence_index": 8
            },
            {
              "sentence_text": "They're buying it.",
              "anchor_speaker": "ALEX",
              "sentence_index": 9
            }
          ],
